3CE is a community-owned public agency
governed by board members who represent
each community served. Sourcing electricity

keep electricity rates competitive for customers,
while also funding innovative energy programs
designed to lower greenhouse gas emissions
and stimulate economic development. 3CE
serves customers in communities throughout
Monterey, San Benito, San Luis Obispo, Santa
Barbara and Santa Cruz counties. Visit

more.
